Package ece325_lab_assignment4

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ZooPerformer
    Interface that will be for anyone performing at a Zoo with animals that need to be fed.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Artist
    Designed to be used with ZooShow class and will be in charge of: Playing music and stopping music.
    recordAnimal  
    showTracker
    This class is designed to check the feeding history at the ZooShow.
    Zoo
    You do not have to make changes to this class.
    ZooAnimal
    Keep track of animal information of a zoo animal.
    ZooShow
    Creates a show object which will create a tracking sheet for tracking animals being fed, as well as creating an Artist object which will play music and feed ZooAnimals.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AlreadyFedException
    Exception used specifically for ece325_lab_assignment4 package and should be thrown if a ZooAnimal requests to be fed more than once in a day.
    NotPlayingException
    Exception used specifically for ece325_lab_assignment4 package where there might be no music playing during a function that requires it.
